            <title>[SOLR-3371] Admin UI breaks with a core named &apos;logging&apos; or &apos;threads&apos;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3371</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you make a core with the name &quot;logging&quot; or &quot;threads&quot; the UI gets confused with the logging or threads page.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems like the ~threads and ~logging should be enough to distinguish&lt;/p&gt;</description>
